    MOVDTRCO, 
    PZFILLR1, 
    PZFILLR2, 
    T01CD, 
    FPRICORC, 
    FPRICOEL, 
    FPRFL1,
	FPRDINTE
) AS 
SELECT 
    PZ_STATO, 
    PZ_NRAZIONE, 
    PZ_DTAZIONE, 
    PZ_USAZIONE, 
    PZ_KEYPRGINVIO, 
    PZ_KEYHEADERFATT, 
    PZ_KEYBODYFATT, 
    PZ_TIPODOC, 
    PZ_AMBIENTE, 
    CAST(PZ_DATA AS DATETIME), 
    PZ_NUMERO, 
    PZ_CLIFOR, 
    PZ_STATOELAB, 
    PZ_GESTIONE, 
    PZ_ERRINT, 
    PZ_DATAPROT, 
    PZ_USERPROT, 
    PZ_CLASPROT, 
    PZ_TIPOPROT, 
    PZ_ANNOPROT, 
    PZ_NUMPROT, 
    PZ_TIPOCF, 
    PZ_SETGEST, 
    PZ_UTEGEST, 
    PZ_DATAACCET, 
    PZ_UTENACCET, 
    PZ_DATACONT, 
    PZ_UTENCONT, 
    PZ_TIPOREGCONT, 
    PZ_NUMREGCONT, 
    PZ_DATAREGCONT, 
    PZ_TIPOCONT, 
    PZ_DATAARCH, 
    PZ_UTENARCH, 
    PZ_TIPOARC, 
    PZ_STATOPROT, 
    PZ_CODSDI, 
    PZ_DATADOCR, 
    PZ_CODCUP, 
    PZ_CODCIG, 
    COALESCE(PQ_IMPTOTDOC, 0), 
    PZ_IMPCALDOC, 
    COALESCE(T5.IMPONIBILE_FATTURA, 0), 
    COALESCE(T5.IMPOSTA_FATTURA, 0), 
    PZ_NOMXML, 
    PZ_DATAORARIC, 
    PZ_DATAORARIC, 
    PZ_DATASTATO, 
    PZ_FMTTRASMISS, 
    PZ_CODDEST, 
    PZ_NOTAFATT, 
    COALESCE(PQ_CAUSALE, ' '), 
    COALESCE(P2_FISCIVACOD, ' '), 
    COALESCE(P2_CODFISCALE, ' '), 
    ( CASE  
      WHEN (COALESCE(P2_ANADENOMIN, ' ')<>' ') THEN COALESCE(P2_ANADENOMIN, ' ') 
      ELSE SUBSTRING(RTRIM(P2_ANACOGNOME)+' '+RTRIM(P2_ANANOME), 1, 80) END 
     ), 
    COALESCE(P2_ANACOGNOME, ' '), 
    COALESCE(P2_ANANOME, ' '), 
    COALESCE(P2_SEDEIND, ' '), 
    COALESCE(P2_SEDENRCIVICO, ' '), 
    COALESCE(P2_SEDECOMUNE, ' '), 
    COALESCE(P2_SEDEPROV, ' '), 
    COALESCE(P2_SEDECAP, 0), 
    COALESCE(T02CD, ' '), 
    COALESCE(T22CD, ' '), 
    COALESCE(T07CD, ' '), 
    COALESCE(MOVNPIVA, 0), 
    COALESCE(MOVDTRCO, PZ_DATAREGCONT), 
    PZ_FILLER1, 
    PZ_FILLER2, 
    PZ_AMBIENTE, 
    ( CASE  
      WHEN (PZ_STATO='A') THEN 'A'  
      WHEN (PZ_STATO='U') THEN 'U'
      WHEN (PZ_STATO='S') THEN 'S'
      WHEN (PZ_STATO='P') THEN 'I'
      WHEN (PZ_ERRINT<>' ') THEN 'E'  
      ELSE 'V'  END
     ) AS FPRICORC, 
    ( CASE  
      WHEN (PZ_STATOPROT='3') THEN 'R'  
      WHEN (PZ_TIPOCONT='C') THEN 'C'
      WHEN (PZ_TIPOCONT='S') THEN 'S'
      WHEN (PZ_TIPOCONT='P') THEN 'P'
      WHEN (PZ_TIPOCONT='E') THEN 'E'
      WHEN (PZ_CLIFOR=' ') THEN 'F' 
      ELSE 'T'  END
     ) AS FPRICOEL,      
     ( CASE  
      WHEN (COALESCE(T5.ALLEGATI_PRESENTI, ' ')='Y') THEN '1'  
      ELSE '0'  END
     ) AS FPRFL1,
	( CASE
	WHEN (PZ_TIPODOC = 'TD16') THEN '1'
	WHEN (PZ_TIPODOC = 'TD17') THEN '1'
	WHEN (PZ_TIPODOC = 'TD18') THEN '1'
	WHEN (PZ_TIPODOC = 'TD19') THEN '1'
	WHEN (PZ_TIPODOC = 'TD20') THEN '1'
	WHEN (PZ_TIPODOC = 'TD21') THEN '1'
	WHEN (PZ_TIPODOC = 'TD22') THEN '1'
	WHEN (PZ_TIPODOC = 'TD23') THEN '1'
	WHEN (PZ_TIPODOC = 'TD27') THEN '1'
	ELSE '0' END
	) AS FPRDINTE
FROM  THIP.FPPRO00F 
LEFT OUTER JOIN THIP.PAA2700F ON 
    PQ_KEYPRGINVIO = PZ_KEYPRGINVIO AND 
    PQ_KEYHEADERFATT = PZ_KEYHEADERFATT AND 
    PQ_KEYBODYFATT = PZ_KEYBODYFATT 
INNER JOIN THIP.PAA0200F ON 
    P2_KEYPRGINVIO = PZ_KEYPRGINVIO AND 
    P2_KEYHEADERFATT = PZ_KEYHEADERFATT AND 
    P2_KEYBODYFATT = PZ_KEYBODYFATT 
LEFT OUTER JOIN FINANCE.BCMOTPT ON 
    T01CD=PZ_AMBIENTE AND 
    T09CD=PZ_TIPOREGCONT AND 
    MOVNUREG=PZ_NUMREGCONT 
LEFT OUTER JOIN THIP.FATTURE_ACQUISTO T5 ON 
    T5.KEYPRGINVIO = PZ_KEYPRGINVIO AND 
    T5.KEYHEADERFATT = PZ_KEYHEADERFATT AND 
    T5.KEYBODYFATT = PZ_KEYBODYFATT

GRANT ALL ON FINANCE.BCFPRVG TO PUBLIC

Elaborazione file comandi K:\ThipRil\FIXWEB\4.7.0\fix\V4R8M0/37570/primrose/script/03ATTRIBUTEREF.SQL.

Elaborazione file comandi K:\ThipRil\FIXWEB\4.7.0\fix\V4R8M0/37659/tddml/RICHIESTA_SERVIZIO_V01.TDDML.
DROP VIEW THIP.RICHIESTA_SERVIZIO_V01
CREATE 
    VIEW THIP.RICHIESTA_SERVIZIO_V01 AS 
SELECT 
    RICH.* , 
    CASE(STATO_RICHIESTA) 
        WHEN 'C' 
        THEN DATEDIFF(dd,COALESCE(DATA_RICHIESTA_CLI, DATA_RICH),(DATA_CHIUSURA)) 
        ELSE DATEDIFF(dd,COALESCE(DATA_RICHIESTA_CLI, DATA_RICH),CURRENT_TIMESTAMP)
    END AS GIORNI_RICH_PEND 
FROM 
    THIP.RICHIESTA_SERVIZIO RICH

		THIP.MODPRO_ATV_RSR.R_PART_PROGRAM AS R_PART_PROGRAM, 
		THIP.MODPRO_ATV_RSR.ESCLUSO_COSTI AS ESCLUSO_COSTI,

		THIP.RISORSE.DESCR_RIDOTTA AS RSR_DESCR_RIDOTTA,

		THIP.RISORSE.R_COMPON_COSTO AS R_COMPON_COSTO

		AND THIP.MODPRO_ATV_RSR.TIPO_RISORSA = THIP.RISORSE.TIPO_RISORSA

		AND THIP.MODPRO_ATV_RSR.R_RISORSA = THIP.RISORSE.ID_RISORSA

    PZ_NOTAFATT, 
    COALESCE(PQ_CAUSALE, ' '), 
    COALESCE(P2_FISCIVACOD, ' '), 
    COALESCE(P2_CODFISCALE, ' '), 
    ( CASE  
      WHEN (COALESCE(P2_ANADENOMIN, ' ')<>' ') THEN COALESCE(P2_ANADENOMIN, ' ') 
      ELSE SUBSTRING(RTRIM(P2_ANACOGNOME)+' '+RTRIM(P2_ANANOME), 1, 80) END 
     ), 
    COALESCE(P2_ANACOGNOME, ' '), 
    COALESCE(P2_ANANOME, ' '), 
    COALESCE(P2_SEDEIND, ' '), 
    COALESCE(P2_SEDENRCIVICO, ' '), 
    COALESCE(P2_SEDECOMUNE, ' '), 
    COALESCE(P2_SEDEPROV, ' '), 
    COALESCE(P2_SEDECAP, 0), 
    COALESCE(T02CD, ' '), 
    COALESCE(T22CD, ' '), 
    COALESCE(T07CD, ' '), 
    COALESCE(MOVNPIVA, 0), 
    CONVERT(DATETIME, CONVERT(DATE, COALESCE(MOVDTRCO, PZ_DATAREGCONT))), 
    PZ_FILLER1, 
    PZ_FILLER2, 
    PZ_AMBIENTE, 
    ( CASE  
      WHEN (PZ_STATO='A') THEN 'A'  
      WHEN (PZ_STATO='U') THEN 'U'
      WHEN (PZ_STATO='S') THEN 'S'
      WHEN (PZ_STATO='P') THEN 'I'
      WHEN (PZ_ERRINT<>' ') THEN 'E'  
      ELSE 'V'  END
     ) AS FPRICORC, 
    ( CASE  
      WHEN (PZ_STATOPROT='3') THEN 'R'  
      WHEN (PZ_TIPOCONT='C') THEN 'C'
      WHEN (PZ_TIPOCONT='S') THEN 'S'
      WHEN (PZ_TIPOCONT='P') THEN 'P'
      WHEN (PZ_TIPOCONT='E') THEN 'E'
      WHEN (PZ_CLIFOR=' ') THEN 'F' 
      ELSE 'T'  END
     ) AS FPRICOEL,      
     ( CASE  
      WHEN (COALESCE(T5.ALLEGATI_PRESENTI, ' ')='Y') THEN '1'  
      ELSE '0'  END
     ) AS FPRFL1,
	( CASE
	WHEN (PZ_TIPODOC = 'TD16') THEN '1'
	WHEN (PZ_TIPODOC = 'TD17') THEN '1'
	WHEN (PZ_TIPODOC = 'TD18') THEN '1'
	WHEN (PZ_TIPODOC = 'TD19') THEN '1'
	WHEN (PZ_TIPODOC = 'TD20') THEN '1'
	WHEN (PZ_TIPODOC = 'TD21') THEN '1'
	WHEN (PZ_TIPODOC = 'TD22') THEN '1'
	WHEN (PZ_TIPODOC = 'TD23') THEN '1'
	WHEN (PZ_TIPODOC = 'TD27') THEN '1'
	ELSE '0' END
	) AS FPRDINTE
FROM  THIP.FPPRO00F 
LEFT OUTER JOIN THIP.PAA2700F ON 
    PQ_KEYPRGINVIO = PZ_KEYPRGINVIO AND 
    PQ_KEYHEADERFATT = PZ_KEYHEADERFATT AND 
    PQ_KEYBODYFATT = PZ_KEYBODYFATT 
INNER JOIN THIP.PAA0200F ON 
    P2_KEYPRGINVIO = PZ_KEYPRGINVIO AND 
    P2_KEYHEADERFATT = PZ_KEYHEADERFATT AND 
    P2_KEYBODYFATT = PZ_KEYBODYFATT 
LEFT OUTER JOIN FINANCE.BCMOTPT ON 
    T01CD=PZ_AMBIENTE AND 
    T09CD=PZ_TIPOREGCONT AND 
    MOVNUREG=PZ_NUMREGCONT 
LEFT OUTER JOIN THIP.FATTURE_ACQUISTO T5 ON 
    T5.KEYPRGINVIO = PZ_KEYPRGINVIO AND 
    T5.KEYHEADERFATT = PZ_KEYHEADERFATT AND 
    T5.KEYBODYFATT = PZ_KEYBODYFATT

GRANT ALL ON FINANCE.BCFPRVG TO PUBLIC

Elaborazione file comandi K:\ThipRil\FIXWEB\4.7.0\fix\V4R8M0/37860/tddml/VARIAZCST_V01.TDDML.
DROP VIEW THIP.VARIAZCST_V01
CREATE VIEW THIP.VARIAZCST_V01 AS SELECT ARTCOS.*, ART.ID_ARTICOLO AS R_ARTICOLO, ART.TIPO_PARTE, ART.R_LINEA_PROD AS R_LINEA_PRODOTTO, ART.R_MACROFAMIGLIA, ART.R_MICROFAMIGLIA, ART.R_SUBFAMIGLIA, ART.R_CLASSE_MERCLG, ART.R_CLS_MATERIALE, ART.R_PIANIFICATORE , ART.R_GRP_PRODOTTO , ART.R_CLASSE_FISCALE , ART.R_CLASSE_A , ART.R_CLASSE_B , ART.R_CLASSE_C , ART.R_CLASSE_D , ART.R_CLASSE_E 
FROM THIP.ARTICOLO_COSTI ARTCOS JOIN THIP.ARTICOLI ART ON ( ARTCOS.ID_AZIENDA = ART.ID_AZIENDA AND ARTCOS.ID_ARTICOLO = ART.ID_ARTICOLO )

Elaborazione file comandi K:\ThipRil\FIXWEB\4.7.0\fix\V4R8M0/37921/sql/UPDATE_CLASS_ROW.SQL.
UPDATE THERA.CLASSRD_ROW 	 
			SET CD_NAME ='Descrizione.Descrizione' , CORR_CLASS_NAME ='DescrizioneInLingua' , CORR_ATTR_NAME ='Descrizione'
			WHERE DEF_SEARCH = 'Y' AND 
			CONCAT(LTRIM(RTRIM(CLASS_NAME)),LTRIM(RTRIM(RELATION_NAME))) IN (SELECT CONCAT(LTRIM(RTRIM(CLASS_NAME)),LTRIM(RTRIM(RELATION_NAME)))  FROM THERA.CLASSRD WHERE CORR_CLASS_NAME = 'UbicazioneLL')

CREATE TABLE THIP.CM_ART_REGIME_OSS
(
   DATA_ORIGIN CHAR(20) NOT NULL,
   RUN_ID INTEGER NOT NULL,
   ROW_ID INTEGER NOT NULL,
   RUN_ACTION CHAR(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT 'I',
   TRASF_STATUS CHAR(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
   ID_AZIENDA CHAR(3) NOT NULL,
   DESCR_RIDOTTA CHAR(15) NOT NULL,
   DESCRIZIONE VARCHAR(35) NOT NULL,
   STATO CHAR(1) NOT NULL,
   R_UTENTE_CRZ CHAR(20),
   TIMESTAMP_CRZ DATETIME NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
   R_UTENTE_AGG CHAR(20),
   TIMESTAMP_AGG DATETIME NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
   ID_ARTICOLO CHAR(25) NOT NULL,
   ID_ASS_IVA CHAR(3) NOT NULL,
   ID_NAZIONE CHAR(3) NOT NULL,
   ID_CONNOTAZ_OSS CHAR(5) NOT NULL
)  ON 'THIP4'
CREATE UNIQUE INDEX CM_ART_REG_OSS_I01 ON THIP.CM_ART_REGIME_OSS (DATA_ORIGIN ASC, RUN_ID ASC, ROW_ID ASC)
CREATE UNIQUE INDEX CM_ART_REG_OSS_I02 ON THIP.CM_ART_REGIME_OSS (DATA_ORIGIN ASC, RUN_ID ASC, ID_AZIENDA ASC, ID_ARTICOLO ASC, ID_ASS_IVA ASC, ID_NAZIONE ASC, ID_CONNOTAZ_OSS ASC)
ALTER TABLE THIP.CM_ART_REGIME_OSS ADD PRIMARY KEY  (DATA_ORIGIN, RUN_ID, ROW_ID)
GRANT ALL ON THIP.CM_ART_REGIME_OSS TO PUBLIC

)  ON 'THIP4'

ALTER TABLE FINANCE.BCF9TPT ADD    PZTIPODC CHAR(4) DEFAULT ' '
UPDATE FINANCE.BCF9TPT SET PZTIPODC =' ' WHERE PZTIPODC IS NULL OR PZTIPODC =''
UPDATE FINANCE.BCF9TPT 
			SET FINANCE.BCF9TPT.PZTIPODC = (SELECT B.F9ICSOS FROM THIP.F9IVA00K B WHERE FINANCE.BCF9TPT.T01CD=B.F9ICSOC AND 
			FINANCE.BCF9TPT.F9PIDPAC = B.F9IIDLA AND FINANCE.BCF9TPT.F9IIDFI = B.F9IIDFI AND 
			FINANCE.BCF9TPT.F9INDOC = B.F9INDOC AND FINANCE.BCF9TPT.F9IUDOC = B.F9IUDOC AND FINANCE.BCF9TPT.F9ICREG = B.F9ICREG AND
			FINANCE.BCF9TPT.F9INPRI = B.F9INPRI)
			WHERE FINANCE.BCF9TPT.PZTIPODC=' ' AND EXISTS(SELECT * FROM THIP.F9IVA00K C WHERE FINANCE.BCF9TPT.T01CD=C.F9ICSOC AND
			FINANCE.BCF9TPT.F9PIDPAC = C.F9IIDLA AND FINANCE.BCF9TPT.F9IIDFI = C.F9IIDFI AND FINANCE.BCF9TPT.F9INDOC = C.F9INDOC AND FINANCE.BCF9TPT.F9IUDOC = C.F9IUDOC)
GRANT ALL ON FINANCE.BCF9TPT TO PUBLIC

(
   ID CHAR(20) NOT NULL,
   DESCRIZIONE CHAR(80) NOT NULL,
   CLASSE_RISORSA VARCHAR(250) NOT NULL,
   RISORSA_ATTIVA CHAR(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT 'Y',
   LOG CHAR(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT 'N',
   STAMPA_HEADER CHAR(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT 'N',
   STAMPA_BODY CHAR(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT 'N',
   MAX_BODY_SIZE INTEGER,
   R_UTENTE_CRZ CHAR(20),
   TIMESTAMP_CRZ DATETIME NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
   R_UTENTE_AGG CHAR(20),
   TIMESTAMP_AGG DATETIME NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP
)

(

(
   ENTITY_ID CHAR(15) NOT NULL,
